Create a Hero Section Include a headline that introduces the product or service. Add a subheadline that provides a short description or value proposition. Include a call -to-action (CTA) button (e.g , "Sign Up Now,“Learn More”).
Build a Responsive Features Section Create a three -column layout to highlight key features. Each column should have: A small icon or image representing the feature. A title for the feature. A short description explaining the feature. Ensure the section adapts to different screen sizes (e.g ., stacks into a single column on mobile)
Design a Footer Section Include contact details (email, phone
